(10-x)^n\equiv x^n\bmod 10
n
(10-x)^n\equiv -x^n\bmod 10
\begin{align*} (10-x)^n&=\sum_{k=0}^n\binom{n}{k}10^{n-k}(-x)^k\\\\ &=\underbrace{10^n-\binom{n}{1}10^{n-1}x+\cdots(-1)^{n-1}\binom{n}{n-1}10x^{n-1}}_{\text{divisible by 10}}+(-1)^nx^n\\\\\\ &\equiv (-1)^nx^n\bmod 10. \end{align*}
